f_{n}(x)
=
n^{2}x\ (1-x)^{n}
0\le x\le 1
f_{n}
f
f_n(x)=n^2x(1-x)^n
x=n^{-1}
n\to\infty
f_n(n^{-1})=n\left(1-\frac 1 n\right)^n
\{f_n\}
[0,1]
n \rightarrow \infty
\sup\limits_{0\leq x\leq 1}\left|f_n(x)-f(x)\right|
\sup_{0\leq x\leq 1}|f_n(x)-f(x) |=\left(1-\frac1{n+1}\right)^n\times\frac{n^2}{n+1}
